## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not capture all aspects of mental health stigma, particularly in diverse cultural contexts. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of mental health research means that new findings may emerge that could alter current understandings of stigma and its effects. Further research, including empirical studies and longitudinal data, would provide a more comprehensive view of the issue.